noise means that, for each pair of nodes in the graph, we keep its
connection status with probability ğ›½ and change its connection status with probability 1 âˆ’ ğ›½. Based on the noise distribution and a base node/graph classifier ğ‘“ (s), we define a smoothed classifier ğ‘”(s) as follows:

ğ‘”(s) = argmax Pr(ğ‘“ (s âŠ• ğœ–) = ğ‘),

